GIVEAWAY TIME!! 🥳

I have been using @cherbeautysg’s DVZ Haircare Set for a week. Personally, I feel that it has helped with fizziness & dryness of my hair, leaving it silky soft & smells extremely pleasant after using it! (Psst. smells very similar to Chanel Chance Eau Frauchie Perfume). I have yet to see any hair growth since it’s only been a week.

In partnership with @cherbeautysg, she will be giving away 5 pieces of Mishang mask each to 2 lucky winners! 😱

1. Simply like this post
2. You must be a follower of both me (@bryanahuang & @cherbeautysg (don’t so bad follow & unfollow later ah we can track... 🤧)
3. Tag 3 friends in the comments section below (multiple entries are allowed) 
Extra chances: 
4. Share this post on your IG stories and tag both me & @cherbeautysg! (IG story must be up for 24 hours & account need to be PUBLIC
5. Purchase any item from @cherbeautysg during this 1 week for an extra chance!

Giveaway will end on 21 May 2359
All the best everyone! 🤩
